<div class="holiday">
	<% if @upcoming_holidays.nil? %>
		<p>Sorry, we don't have a list of holidays in <span class="country"><%= @country %></span> yet. You can add your country's holidays to the list maintained by the <%= link_to "holidays", "https://github.com/alexdunae/holidays/tree/master/data" %> project on GitHub.</p>
	<% else %>
		<p>The next holiday in <span class="country"><%= @country %></span> is <%= @next_holiday_name %> on <%= @next_holiday_week_day %>, <%= @next_holiday_month %> <%= @next_holiday_month_day %>, <%= @current_year %></p>	
	<% end -%>
</div>
